data.mcp-configuration#MCP configuration:
To connect an MCP client, add this to your MCP config:
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "contextd": {
      "command": "contextd",
      "args": ["serve", "--port", "3333"]
    }
  }
}
See the MCP Server page for more details.

data.configuring-claude-code#Configuring Clau:
Add an .mcp.json file to your project root:
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "contextd": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["contextd", "serve"]
    }
  }
}

data.configuring-cursor#Configuring Cursor:
Add the server to Cursor's MCP settings:
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "contextd": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["contextd", "serve"]
    }
  }
}
